1. INTRODUCTION

You have been chosen as manager  of  a  third division team in the new
British League, can  you  rise  to  the  challenge?   Do  you have the
passion and ability to turn a  team  of  slackers into a mighty force?
Will you make  other  teams  weep  at  the  thought  of  visiting your
stadium?

Your new boss, the director  of  the  club,  has given you his orders.
Take the club to the top of the British Premier League, win the FA Cup
and the British League Cup.

In this demo version you can only  play one full season, then the game
will restart.

You have £500,000 at your  disposal.  It  probably isn`t enough to buy
the championship. You`ll have to use tactics and skill to build a team
worthy of the Premier League title. Good luck.

